Opening your RStudio Project &lt;just link to lesson??&gt;
As a reminder, whenever you are working on scripts within an RStudio Project, you need to open the RStudio Project first and then open the script file from within the RStudio Project.
 
Three ways to open your RStudio Project are mentioned in the RStudio Projects tutorial &lt;relink&gt;
 
Note: you can open up multiple RStudio Projects in RStudio by clicking Session -&gt; New Session.This will open up a new, and separate, RStudio window.
